paragraph.content:
in relation to an application for the approval of the nomination of an
                        additional individual under section 24(1) of that Regulation,
                        means the individual;

subsection.def:
register (名冊) means
                the register of minor works contractors kept under section 8A(1)(c) of
                the Ordinance;

registered minor works
                    contractor (註冊小型工程承建商) means a person
                whose name is for the time being on the register;

registered minor works
                    contractor (provisional) (臨時註冊小型工程承建商)
                means a person whose name is for the time being on the provisional register;

paragraph.def:
class I minor works (第I級別小型工程) means any item of minor works
                    specified in Division 1 of Part 3 of Schedule 1 to the Minor Works
                    Regulation;

class II minor works (第II級別小型工程) means any item of minor works
                    specified in Division 2 of Part 3 of Schedule 1 to that
                    Regulation;

paragraph.content:
in the case of a proposed class I authorized
                    signatory,
                    $2,440;

if the highest class of minor works for which the person is registered is class
                I,
                $595;

if the highest class of minor works for which the person is registered is class
                II, $595;
                or

if the highest class of minor works to which the application relates is class
                I,
                $1,130;

if the highest class of minor works to which the application relates is class
                II, $835;
                or

if the highest class of minor works to which the application relates is class
                I,
                $1,300;

if the highest class of minor works to which the application relates is class
                II, $915;
                or

in the case of a proposed class I authorized
                    signatory,
                    $2,700;

if the individual is a proposed class I authorized
                signatory,
                $2,700;

if the individual is a proposed class II authorized
                signatory, $965;
